715239f.title: Manhattan: 121st Street - 3rd Avenue
715239f.text:
121st Street at the N.W. corner of Third Ave. Building referred
to is the Firet Collegiate Dutch Reformed Church of Harlem and was
dedicated in 1835.
About 1880.
